com.yworks.yfiles.graphml

Class QueryOutputHandlersEventArgs

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.graphml.QueryOutputHandlersEventArgs
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEventArgs

    public final class QueryOutputHandlersEventArgs
extends Object
implements IEventArgs
    Event argument implementation that is used by the QueryOutputHandlers event.

    These event arguments can be used to add more IOutputHandler implementations to the GraphMLWriter dynamically at the time of writing, by adding them to the Handlers collection.

    See Also:
    GraphMLIOHandler
